                            'Eclairium'  1.02

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  @{" Eclairium " link play} is a Workbench game where you send lightning bolts to
eliminate various tiles that have coloured shapes on them... and
the more tiles of the same type you eliminate, the more points you
get.

  One catch is that, as real lightning, the lightning bolts you
send are unpredictable and you will never really know where they
will go...

  Have fun!

